  <brief_title>Gemcitabine and Cisplatin in Treating Patients With Metastatic Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of Gemcitabine (GEMZAR) and Cisplatin (CDDP) in Advanced Breast Cancer</official_title>
